* [sol1-Python3]

```python
class Solution:
    def alternateDigitSum(self, n: int) -> int:
        ans, sign = 0, 1
        for c in str(n):
            x = int(c)
            ans += sign * x
            sign *= -1
        return ans
```

* [sol1-Java]

```java
class Solution {
    public int alternateDigitSum(int n) {
        int ans = 0, sign = 1;
        for (char c : String.valueOf(n).toCharArray()) {
            int x = c - '0';
            ans += sign * x;
            sign *= -1;
        }
        return ans;
    }
}
```

